<h2 style="margin:0 0 10px 0; font-size:22px; font-weight:600;">
    Contract Terminated
</h2>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:25px 0;">
    Hello {{homeBuyerName}},
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    This email confirms that your mortgage contract has been officially terminated and closed.
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    <strong>Final Contract Summary:</strong>
</p>

<table style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0; border-collapse:collapse;">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Contract Number:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;"><strong>{{contractNumber}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Property:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{propertyName}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Contract Start Date:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{startDate}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Termination Date:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{terminationDate}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Total Payments Made:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{totalPaymentsMade}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Total Amount Paid:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{totalAmountPaid}}</td>
    </tr>
</table>

{{#if refundStatus}}
<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:15px 0;">
    <strong>Refund Status:</strong> {{refundStatus}}
</p>
{{/if}}

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    All records related to this contract have been updated. You can still access your historical data through your dashboard for reference purposes.
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Thank you for being a part of the {{projectName}} community. If you ever decide to pursue homeownership again, we would be honored to assist you.
</p>

<a href="{{dashboardLink}}"
    style="color:#ffffff; padding:8px 20px; text-decoration:none; font-size:14px; font-family:Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:12px; display:inline-block; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #049DC8 0%, #0082B5 100%); border: none; margin-top:15px;">
    View Contract History
</a>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:20px; margin-top:30px;">
    Best, <br />
    The {{projectName}} Team.
</p>
